  "texts": [
    "Additionally, as students in the metaverse move from a static to a dynamic learning environment, and become the focal point of the teaching-learning process, it is necessary to develop new pedagogical and methodological paradigms compatible with the metaverse technology.",
    "PEU is another crtical factor that facilitate the adoption of metaverse-based leraning.",
    "Hence, Thus, it is important to ensure that the metaverse-based learning platform is user-friendly and intuitive.",
    "If the platform is difficult to navigate or use, users may not perceive it as useful.",
    "Thus, it is essential to design the platform with user experience in mind, provide clear instructions and tutorials, and make sure that all the features are easily accessible."
  ]
}